{
  "id": 5084062739988480,
  "name": "Support the `hanging` and `each-line` for the `text-indent` property",
  "summary": "The two optional keywords for the `text-indent` property extends the capability and the usability of the property.\n\nThe `hanging` keyword changes indentation to \"hanging\", that is, all lines except the first line will be indented.\n\nThe `each-line` keyword makes indentation to affect not only the first line but also each line after a forced line break.",
